name: Super Britten Bros. (24-Hr. Game Demo)
description: This is a platformer created by Britten Spandley for his Computer Science 2 project report. Created in 24 hours, this tech demo was made to show how much a novice to average programmer can create in said time. Enjoy the game, and sorry it's poorly made. I would love to revisit it later on and clean up code/sounds/sprites/etc.
